15 after-hours release of nonconsensual towed vehicles, including
16 incorporated and unincorporated areas, by a wrecker or towing
17 service licensed by the Department of Public Safety Labor and repair
18 facilities as defined in Section 953 of Title 15 of the Oklahoma
19 Statutes. No wrecker or towing service or repair facilities shall
20 charge any fee for nonconsensual towed vehicles and storage which
21 exceeds the maximum rates established by the Commission Board. Such
22 rates shall be in addition to any other rates, fees or charges
23 authorized, allowed or required by law, including environmental
24 remediation fees and services.
